[[File:Art Jogja 2013 Taman Budaya Yogyakarta.jpg|thumb|250px|Art Jog 2013]]
'''Art Jog''' is a [[contemporary art]] [[fair]], held annually in [[Taman Budaya Yogyakarta]], [[Indonesia]].<ref name="aj">{{cite web|publisher= Art Jogja|accessdate=14 May 2014|title= Art Jog 2014|url= http://artfairjogja.com/web/?lang=en}}</ref> The fair started out in 2008 as part of the Yogyakarta Art Festival.<ref name="asa">{{cite web|publisher= Art Radar Asia|title= Art Jog ’12: Fresh contemporary art makes for meaningful Indonesian fair|accessdate= 14 May 2014|url= http://artradarjournal.com/2012/07/18/art-jog-12-fresh-contemporary-art-makes-for-meaningful-indonesian-fair/}}</ref> The Jogja Art Fair became independent in 2009, and changed its name to Art Jog in 2010.<ref name="asa"/>

